pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Eby'amawulire ebiragibwa ku daasiboodi eno bikuŋŋaanyizibwa butereevu okuva mu kuddamu okunoonyereza era tebiva mu nnamba z'ensi ez'ekitongole oba ebiwandiiko. Kikiikirira ebirowoozo abavubuka bye baayogera mu kiseera ky'okunoonyereza era ebyo byonna ebiva mu kuddamu bino buvunaanyizibwa bw'omukozi so si PMNCH. PMNCH yeemalidde ku kussa ekitiibwa, okutumbula n'okukuuma eddembe n'obulamu bw'abantu bonna. Endowooza yonna eyogerwako mu kuddamu okunoonyereza oba ebintu ebifulumizibwa ebiva mu daasiboodi eno ebikontana n'obweyamo buno tebikkirizibwa PMNCH.

wra03a-subtext: Okufuna obusobozi bw'okufuna eby'okuddamu obukadde 1.2 okuyitira mu daasiboodi eno ey'enjawulo, ekyuma eky'enjawulo ekigatta amaloboozi g'abakyala n'abawala n'obusobozi kumpi obutaliiko kkomo obw'okwekenneenya digito.
pmn01a-subtext: Bye bye Enkola eno ey'okukubaganya ebirowoozo ewa ekifaananyi eky'okuddamu n'amagezi bye tukuŋŋaanya okuva mu bavubuka abali wakati w'emyaka 10-24 okwetooloola ensi yonna. Ensonga enkulu mu kaweefube ono kwe kubuuza ekibuuzo eky'obwereere: "Okulongoosa obulamu bwange, njagala...". Abavubuka okuva mu nsi yonna babadde baddamu kino, nga batuwa amagezi ag'enjawulo ku byetaago byabwe, essuubi lyabwe n'ebyo bye baagala. Okunoonyereza ku nsonga eno, okuzuula ebyafaayo ebiri emabega w'ennamba zino, era weegatta ku kugaziya amaloboozi g'abavubuka obuwumbi 1.8 mu nsi yonna. Okumanya ebisingawo ku kampeyini eno, genda http://www.1point8.org.
